[  8204] By: jhi                                   on 2000/12/19  22:58:18
        Log: Recode the naughty binary bytes ([\x00-\x08\x0b-\x1f\x7f-\xff])
             using the \xHH notation.  No more inlined UTF-8, sigh, but easier
             on editors and diffing/patching.
     Branch: perl
	   ! t/op/utf8decode.t
