             Subject: [PATCH 5.6.0]subprocess fixup for threads
             From: Dan Sugalski <dan@sidhe.org>
             To: perl5-porters@perl.org
             Date: Tue, 11 Apr 2000 17:02:32 -0400
             Message-Id: <4.3.0.20000411170218.01d2f580@24.8.96.48>
             
